<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.8.6">
<l>cevikaḷā lāraniṉ kīrttik kaṉiyeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>kavikaḷē kālappaṇ ṭēṉaṟaip pattuṟṟu</l>
<l>puviyiṉmēl poṉneṭuñ cakkarat tuṉṉaiyē</l>
<l>yaviviṉṟi yātarik kumeṉa tāviyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Absorbing [it] fully with the ears when the poems that speak</l>
<l>of the fruit of your fame timely drip with melodious honey,</l>
<l>apart from annihilation my soul craves</l>
<l>only for you with the golden large discus on earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
